![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a3081d44-2739-48ce-a330-970c7c808f4f/Screenshot_20240701_170248.jpg?format=original)

Jey Uso opens the show with a promo about how he's going to win MITB.

Chad Gable in inturrupts to say HE is the one who's going to win. Uso asks didn't Gable get got by the Wyatts? Gable says it should be Jey they chase because he stole the fireflies. They start to fight.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f6b729c9-afee-4923-827a-74d87eb6ea67/Screenshot_20240701_171149.jpg?format=original)

LIGHTS OUT. THE WYATT 6 ARE HERE.

They play with Gable and chase him off before dropping off another package to the announce table.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1f517cc7-c8b9-4811-ab7f-85abf2667b90/Screenshot_20240701_171258.jpg?format=original)

